\mainpage Android Framework

**Android Framework** (AF)  is the full collection of Android API, Modules and entry-point required for a Game to port an iOS application to Android. The exposure comes 100% through C++, and completly eliminates the need for Java code at game-side level.
The Android Framework repository also comes with a complete set of tools for building an android project.


More information can be found on the [Gameloft Docs](https://docs.gameloft.org/android-framework/).

